verbose_text: Under normoxic culture onditions, TGFBR2 was significantly expressed at a higher level under IGF-1 stimulation compared to the sole stimulation with TGF-beta1 at all measured time points and compared to the combined stimulation TGF-beta1 and IGF-1 after 24 and 48 h (all : P = 0.043) (XREF_FIG).
